OL,6,F"Time is money. When you're trying to
OL,7,Fbuild an affordable housing project,
OL,8,Fand things are taking a lot longer
OL,9,Fthan they should even after you've got
OL,10,Fplanning permission, the cost of that
OL,11,Fultimately affects the cost of housing.
OL,13,F"One of the biggest driving factors of
OL,14,Fthe cost to build a unit of housing is
OL,15,Fthe financial costs associated with
OL,16,Fthe planning system."
OL,18,FCharity representatives are also
OL,19,Fspeaking about the burden of costs
OL,20,Fcreated by the system.
