OL,3,CCalls for changes to Jersey's complex
OL,4,Cplanning system
OL,6,FAndrew Lewis, chairman of the St
OL,7,FHelier Youth and Community Trust, says
OL,8,Ftoo much of his charity's funds are
OL,9,Fspent on fees associated with seeking
OL,10,Fplanning permission.
OL,12,FHe says: "What (the department) is not
OL,13,Fdoing is asking whether they actually
OL,14,Fneed all of the planning policies and
OL,15,Fregulations and considering which ones
OL,16,Fthey could do without.
OL,18,F"When it comes to the third sector,
OL,19,Fall it does is add extra costs."
