OL,3,CCalls for changes to Jersey's complex
OL,4,Cplanning system
OL,6,FWhilst charities are given a discount
OL,7,Fon planning fees, additional costs are
OL,8,Fincurred when they must pay people -
OL,9,Fsuch as surveyors, architects, and
OL,10,Flandscape architects - to complete the
OL,11,Fnecessary forms for an application.
OL,13,FConstable Philip le Sueur, of Jersey's
OL,14,FPlanning Committee, says the
OL,15,F'complicated' planning process is a
OL,16,Fnecessary evil due to Jersey's size.
